cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on personalized response generation for conversational systems using sequence to sequence learning. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a two-phase approach to model the responding style of humans and generate personalized responses. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses the encoder-decoder framework for sequence to sequence learning. 
4. cs.SD (Sound) is less likely but still possible as the paper may involve speech recognition and synthesis for conversational systems. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also less likely but possible as the paper proposes a novel human aided method for evaluating the performance of personalized response generation models.
